    We set the body to have no margin and to hide overflow so that the video covers the entire viewport.
    
    The section element is given a position: relative; style, which allows us to position the h1 element relative to it.
    
    The video is set to have a width of 100% and to maintain its aspect ratio while covering the entire width of its container.
    
    The h1 element is positioned absolutely within the section, and top: 50%; and left: 50%; are used to center it both vertically and horizontally. transform: translate(-50%, -50%); is used to offset the element by half of its own width and height to center it precisely.
    
    We added some additional styles for text appearance, such as color, font-size, and text-transform.
    
    
     -->
    




